      "span_text": "Since the exact sub-graph isomorphism on general graphs is inherently a NP problem, many research efforts have been devoted to some restricted classes of graphs such as trees, two-connected outer-planar graphs, and two-connected series-parallel graphs and graphs of bounded tree-width"
